Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一台機體  就想同Virtue對抗嗎
