Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到…聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你搗亂的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  那時的…女人的聲音！
