Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵人開炮後開始作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然小看我！
