Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
