Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然在作戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快前往回收Kyrios和Virtue
