Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞…
