Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  前方有物體接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的嗎
