Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請記得為我報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你擊毀少尉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事  一般兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個有生命的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明中尉
