Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快撤退  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓男人的覺悟付諸東流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  丟下同伴跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作風一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  你們會遭報應的
