Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到我才這樣做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣做！
