Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興吧  阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  明中尉被…
