Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼  哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想要那樣殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的…本質嗎
