Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了Nadleeh嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  Nadleeh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios發現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了  這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…無可救藥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格所追求的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam正在體現著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  為什麼Meister們這麼不完全呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是監視者而非執行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的就是繼續注視著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是通往毀滅的道路
